Advantage of Selenium   

--------------------

1.  Open source.

2.  Works on multiple OS(Windows, mac, Linux etc).

3.  Works on almost all browser(Edge, Chrome, Safari, Opera, Firefox)

4.  It supports multiple progamming language(Java, C#, Ruby, Python, PHP, and pearl etc).

5.  Set of libraries(which required less space 20-25 MB).
